  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc0 \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dc5\u0db3\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dd6 \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca \u0d86\u0db7\u0dbb\u0dab \u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The gold ornaments worn by the Mother of God were stolen",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Marandankeni Police, yesterday (17th) some group stole the ornaments worn by the Mother of God in a Catholic church located in Katteikadu area of \u200b\u200bEast Vadamarachchi, Jaffna.",
        "The annual service of the church was held on the last 14th and 15th and the police suspect that a large number of people participated in the annual service on those days and that some of the people who participated in it may have stolen the relevant gold ornaments.",
        "It has not yet been revealed who stole the gold ornaments worn by the Goddess and the priests of the church have complained to the police that the Goddess was not harmed and only the gold ornaments were missing.",
        "The Marandankeni police further said that the stolen armor is worth nearly 30 lakh rupees and that a wide investigation has been started to find the suspects."
      ],
